Signed-off-by: Matheus Sampaio Queiroga <srherobrine20@gmail.com>
---
 drivers/net/ethernet/airoha/airoha_eth.c  |  19 +-
 drivers/net/ethernet/airoha/airoha_npu.c  | 360 ++++++++++++++--------
 include/linux/soc/airoha/airoha_offload.h |  24 ++
 3 files changed, 273 insertions(+), 130 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/net/ethernet/airoha/airoha_eth.c b/drivers/net/ethernet/airoha/airoha_eth.c
index 8d5b3871e..c4d798b8b 100644
--- a/drivers/net/ethernet/airoha/airoha_eth.c
